attributes.background:
With the absurdly disproportionate and hysterical response in Sudan & among many misinformed and extremist elements elsewhere in the world, including the UK to the agreement of Liverpool teacher Gillian Gibbons to allow her class to name a Teddy Bear Mohammed after a child in her class;

The PM should publicly support the campaign to Ask everyone who gives or recieves a Teddy Bear or similar toy to a child this year to name it GILLIAN as a gesture of support for this poor woman and against barbarism and hysterical bigotry.



Please support Gillian by signing up - Thank You
